typeDescriptions.typeString: literal_string "It allows both accredited and non-accredited investors to contribute into the STO. Non-accredited investors will be capped at a maximum investment limit (as a default or specific to their jurisdiction). Tokens will be sold according to tiers sequentially & each tier has its own price and volume of tokens to sell. Upon receipt of funds (ETH, POLY or DAI), security tokens will automatically transfer to investors wallet address"

rightHandSide.value: It allows both accredited and non-accredited investors to contribute into the STO. Non-accredited investors will be capped at a maximum investment limit (as a default or specific to their jurisdiction). Tokens will be sold according to tiers sequentially & each tier has its own price and volume of tokens to sell. Upon receipt of funds (ETH, POLY or DAI), security tokens will automatically transfer to investors wallet address
